{"tid":1896340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新冠肺炎：周三起限口罩及搓手液出口至4月底","createTime":"2020-02-25T05:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T05:40:20.000Z","uid":244704,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe637367acd1fe6f2173122e5150d1ccb12c8f8","tid":1896340,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎在南韓廣泛傳播，該國掀起口罩慌。南韓政府周二（25日）宣布，周三（26日）凌晨零時起限制口罩、搓手液等防疫用品出口，直至4月30日。<br />\n食品醫藥品安全處處長李義表示，政府決定於周三起「原則上」禁止口罩出口，出口量限制在當日產量10%以內，並規定生產量一半以上的口罩必須供應給南韓郵政等公共營運商。所有生產商必須每日向政府通報生產量及國內運輸情況，若同一筆交易牽涉1萬個口罩亦要上報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200225/mobile/bkn-20200225131332992-0225_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200225%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200225131332992-0225_00912_001.html&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=c60720ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200225/mobile/bkn-20200225131332992-0225_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"179cd4e4ead5a7082fa8224e382f3bbb88067417","tid":1896340,"uid":189157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b4ff69cc25f9b2b7087f0fa7f499c2f6eaec24ff","tid":1896340,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"香港可以高價賣番比佢地"},{"pid":"77bd91b1b38a030d7e43e0fc8ebe6e52428e8582","tid":1896340,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢</span>肺炎"},{"pid":"79ebb3938e6d830eab97588a84ce25c30a650aa9","tid":1896340,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4ff69cc25f9b2b7087f0fa7f499c2f6eaec24ff","tid":1896340,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"香港可